## V11 Done Definition

V11 can only be considered meaningfully advanced when:

- P0 hardening items have clear observed behavior
- duplicate behavior is deterministic
- replay attempts fail secure
- mismatch attempts fail secure
- timeout and ambiguity fail secure
- durable state failure does not create false trust
- access unlock guard still holds
- public verify unknown/mismatched pair does not show active verified trust
- safe error scan passes
- limitations are documented
- no production/audit/partnership claim is added

